-I know.

105
00:07:27,405 --> 00:07:29,115
Here you go. Eat up.

106
00:07:32,410 --> 00:07:36,247
I heard Yoon-seo doesn't
even take a lot of after-school classes.

107
00:07:36,330 --> 00:07:37,373
