Sorry for not telling you sooner.

135
00:08:56,911 --> 00:08:58,454
Getting our kids' names

136
00:08:58,538 --> 00:09:00,957
in a professor's thesis
will open many doors for them.

137
00:09:01,499 --> 00:09:02,917
They all do it.

138
00:09:03,751 --> 00:09:05,836
Only those without
connections can't do it.

139
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:08,965
Why would you say no
when the opportunity is given to you?

140
00:09:09,632 --> 00:09:11,968
I appreciate the offer,

141
00:09:12,468 --> 00:09:13,594
but I'll pass.

142
00:09:14,804 --> 00:09:15,680
Do you mean that?

143
00:09:16,264 --> 00:09:17,139
Yes.

144
00:09:18,516 --> 00:09:19,559
I'll get going then.

145
00:09:20,893 --> 00:09:23,104
Okay. I have patients
in the afternoon too.

146
00:09:23,854 --> 00:09:24,814
See you next time.

147
00:09:26,857 --> 00:09:27,900
Bye.

148
