Of course I did.

163
00:10:42,725 --> 00:10:44,894
I actually had lunch outside.

164
00:10:44,977 --> 00:10:47,146
But she wouldn't have eaten if I didn't.

165
00:10:47,229 --> 00:10:48,731
That's why I ate.

166
00:10:49,565 --> 00:10:51,776
However, your food tasted so good

167
00:10:51,859 --> 00:10:53,611
that I just couldn't stop.

168
00:10:54,487 --> 00:10:56,822
I thought I'd never be able
to cook like Joong-do's mom.

169
00:10:56,906 --> 00:10:59,659
-Maybe I'm close now.
-Why would you compare yourself to her?

170
00:10:59,742 --> 00:11:03,454
She has her style,
and you have your own as well.

171
00:11:03,537 --> 00:11:05,706
