172
00:11:06,540 --> 00:11:08,000
-Were you grocery shopping?
-Yes.

173
00:11:08,084 --> 00:11:10,169
I want to make some short ribs
for Ji-hoon.

174
00:11:10,252 --> 00:11:12,588
Lucky him.

175
00:11:13,297 --> 00:11:14,548
I should get going now.

176
00:11:14,632 --> 00:11:17,176
