197
00:12:19,363 --> 00:12:23,242
No, I'm not talking about money.
I mean she's very happy.

198
00:12:28,789 --> 00:12:29,623
Good job.

199
00:12:31,375 --> 00:12:33,043
-One, two, three.
-One, two, three.

