-Hello.
-Hye-joo, long time no see.

202
00:12:38,090 --> 00:12:39,467
Have you been well?

203
00:12:39,550 --> 00:12:40,801
Yes. How about you?

204
00:12:40,885 --> 00:12:43,345
We've been good as always.

205
00:12:45,264 --> 00:12:46,599
Oh, these?

206
00:12:46,682 --> 00:12:48,642
We still receive them
along with some cash.

207
00:12:49,351 --> 00:12:50,853
The donor is still anonymous.

208
00:12:50,936 --> 00:12:53,314
We were too busy this morning,

209
00:12:53,397 --> 00:12:55,524
so we're finally moving them in now.

210
00:12:55,608 --> 00:12:56,692
Then let me help.

211
00:12:56,775 --> 00:12:57,902
-No.
-No.

212
00:12:59,236 --> 00:13:00,154
