213
00:13:02,490 --> 00:13:04,909
All right. I'll call before
I stop by next time.

214
00:13:04,992 --> 00:13:07,495
Okay. Call and stop by
when we're not too busy.

215
00:13:07,578 --> 00:13:09,997
I will. See you next time.

216
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,790
